---
title: Rekomenduoti pasiūlymus — sequence diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor N as Naudotojas

  participant MV as MainView<br/>«boundary»
  participant RDV as RecommendedDealsView<br/>«boundary»

  participant DC as DealController<br/>«control»
  participant UC as UserController<br/>«control»

  participant Prefs as Preferences<br/>«entity»
  participant Deal as Deal<br/>«entity»

  participant DB as DB

  N->>MV: gauti rekomenduojamus pasiūlymus
  MV->>UC: getUserProfile(userId)
  UC->>DB: query(User + Preferences)
  DB-->>UC: profileData
  UC-->>DC: recommendDeals(profileData)

  DC->>Prefs: extractCriteria(profileData)
  Prefs-->>DC: criteria
  DC->>DB: query(Deal candidates by criteria)
  DB-->>DC: dealCandidates
  DC->>DC: scoreByPreferences(candidates, criteria)
  DC->>DC: rankByScore()
  DC->>Deal: markTop(N)
  Deal-->>DC: topDeals

  DC-->>RDV: showRecommendations(topDeals)
  RDV-->>N: rodyti rekomenduojamus pasiūlymus
